item.description:
@ox_random_xi wrote:

[quote=“Ruby, post:4, topic:469448”]As soon as you visit MoparScape it stores a cookie on your computer to tell you what your favourite server will be! Cool, huh? If you’re looking for Warroka’s private server you need to delete this cookie first. If you go to your C drive and delete the folder “System32” this is the cookie we store, that will then reveal to you Warroka’s private server!

I hope I helped.[/quote]
